title: SBI Shinsei Bank Soars 11% From IPO Price in Tokyo Trading Debut
description: SBI Shinsei Bank Ltd. surged as much as 11% in its trading debut in Tokyo on Wednesday after raising ¥322 billion yen ($2.1 billion) in Japan’s second-biggest initial public offering of the year.
